<outline text="Service-oriented (SaaS): This might be more complex than our game as we are only interested in protecting an asset (Cloud storage)."/>
<outline text="They obtain some information on $$T$$ as an outcome of the signalling game analysis"/>
<outline text="We assume we know the trust level $$T$$."/>
