                            <outline text="Possible Extensions">
<outline text="Use a Repeated game for the AD-game"/>
<outline text="We could use our scenario with selfish (internal attacker) or trusted cloud (without external attacker) for a simple signalling game (Demonstration for Monday)"/>
<outline text="Replace AD-game with other static games for different types of cloud deployment models"/>
