<outline text="PARAMETRISED SECURITY LEVEL GAME #h">
    <outline text="Utility Function Definitions">
        <outline text="Generic #tt">
            <outline text="$$u^{{d,a}}_D = (l(\gamma) - 1) L - \kappa(\gamma) &amp;lt; 0$$ #GT"/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{d,a}}_A = (1 - (l(\gamma)) B - A &amp;lt;0$$ #GT"/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{12}}_D = -\kappa(\gamma)$$ #GT"/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{12}}_A = 0$$ #GT"/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{21}}_D = -L &amp;lt; 0$$. #GT"/>
            <outline text="********$$u^{{21}}_A = B - A &amp;gt;0$$ -- Attack cost $$A &amp;gt;= 0$$ #GT******** "/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{22}}_D = 0$$ #GT"/>
            <outline text="$$u^{{22}}_A = 0$$ #GT"/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="Finally, in the case where both the defender and attacker do not perform an action, then neither player gains nor loses: $$u^{{-d,-a}}_D = 0$$ and $$u^{{-d,-a}}_A = 0$$ respectively. #cyber-SA-17 #GT"/>
        <outline text="The defender's utility $$u^{{d,a}}_D = (l(\gamma) - 1) L - \kappa(\gamma) &amp;lt; 0$$ is a cost function, consisting of the defense of the asset using a control of a certain strength $$l(\gamma)$$, is where $$\kappa$$ is the defense cost using a specific control. #GT #cyber-SA-17"/>
        <outline text="$$u^{{-d,a}}_A = B - A $$ #cyber-SA-17 #GT"/>
        <outline text="********In the following attacker's utility: $$u^{{11}}_A = (1 - (l(\gamma)) B - A &amp;lt;0$$, there exist a defense mechanism while an attacker is launching an attack.******** "/>
        <outline text="When there are no controls for defending an asset, the defender suffers an impact loss affecting the asset: $$u^{{-d,a}}_D = -L &amp;lt; 0$$. #cyber-SA-17 #GT"/>
        <outline text="The defender has specific controls in place, but there is no attack. Hence,  $$u^{{d,-a}}_D = -\kappa(\gamma)$$ is the cost of defense using a specific control. #GT #cyber-SA-17"/>
        <outline text="There is no attack, so there is neither a benefit nor a cost for the attacker ($$u^{{d,-a}}_A = 0$$). #GT #cyber-SA-17"/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="Utility Matrix">
        <outline text="\[\begin{array}{ |c|c|c| }\hline&amp;amp; s^{a}_A \quad(\mbox{attack}) &amp;amp; s^{-a}_A \quad(\mbox{not attack}) \\\hline s^{d}_D \quad(\mbox{defend}) &amp;amp; (l - 1)L - c_D, (1 - l)L - c_A &amp;amp; -c_D, 0 \\\hline s^{-d}_D \quad(\mbox{not defend}) &amp;amp; -L, L-c_A &amp;amp; 0, 0 \\ \hline\end{array}\]"/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="Equilibrium Analysis"/>
</outline>
